<div class="container">
    
    <div class="form-wrapper">
    
    <div class="row mb40 mt20">

        <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1"> 
            
            <h2>What are your college cost needs?</h2>
            
                <form action="">
                    
                     <p>About how much do you think you'll need to fill your cost-of-college gap?</p>
                    
                        <hr>    
                             <p>Fundraising Goal (can change later)</p>
                           
                                <div class="radio">
                                <label><input type="radio" name="optradio" value="">500</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="radio">
                                <label><input type="radio" name="optradio" value="">1000</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="radio">
                                <label><input type="radio" name="optradio" value="">2000</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="radio">
                                <label><input type="radio" name="optradio" value="">5000</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="radio">
                                <label><input type="radio" name="optradio" value="">10000</label>
                                </div>
                          
                        <hr> 
                            <p>What do you need funds for at this time? (can change later)</p>
                    
                                <div class="checkbox">
                                <label><input type="checkbox" value="">Tuition (portion of)</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="checkbox">
                                 <label><input type="checkbox" value="">Living expenses</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="checkbox">
                                <label><input type="checkbox" value="">Books</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="checkbox">
                                <label><input type="checkbox" value="">Lab fees of software</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="checkbox">
                                <label><input type="checkbox" value="">Other</label>
                                </div>
                    
                    
                        <hr> 
            <p>To use GreenNote, you must be asking for funding specifically for school, and be enrolled to attend a college in the United States</p>
                    
                                <div class="checkbox">
                                <label><input type="checkbox" value="">I'll be using these funds for college, not for personal use</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="checkbox">
                                 <label><input type="checkbox" value="">I'm currently accepted to or enrolled in a U.S. college</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="checkbox">
                                <label><input type="checkbox" value="">I have already applied for a financial aid, and looked at other scholarchip or grant opportunities</label>
                                </div>
                            


                        
                        <div class="mt40">
                            {{> atoms/button modifierClass="default-button" title="next" }}

                        </div>
                    
                    </form>
                    

                </div>

        </div>

    </div>
    
</div>    